post.body: Ah, finally setup a domain with NameCoin and everything for my new blog.

Bad news, I lost access to my ZeroNet websites, [badprogramming.bit](/1N76xe65TdeiA2SkVKSeX2WQPyCSzdw5az), and [gauched.badprogramming.bit](/15SuecY2MVYyBbJUBTyt4C8DZvifS5kJKc).

I'm sure nobody cares, but it's because I was messing with ZeroNet and ended up getting the dreaded "DatabaseError: database disk image is malformed" message. Anyways, I had to set ZeroNet up again. (Even though it meant losing my sites.)

Anyways, I've made new sites for [badprogramming.bit](/1FZeZMLx4Bi78SW5r1TFh8fxkPdieNcpk4) and [gauched.badprogramming.bit](/1D9bycLGS34xwgTX7u29eqzUYD7DEbT2r7), so please use those from now on. I'll update the NameCoin domain today, and hopefully find some way to salvage the private keys to the old sites and add redirects.

Moral of the Story: Back up content.db.
Alright, updated the NameCoin domain. Now I just have to wait for this all to update and stuff.
I forgot the private keys for the sites are in users.json. (I'm a dumbass.) Anyways, it's a bit late now so whatever, i'll add the redirect.
Debating whether the donation thing that nobody is going to use should be the 2nd or 3rd thing on my homepage. Eh, whatever.

Ah, some peers are finally on muh blog!
Big improvement from yesterday, when my old blog had 60 peers and my new blog had zero. xD

PaintNinja's NinjaBeats streamer is pretty freaking awesome. :-D
[Works great!](/15F9LYs6c17NUXv3MxpJSGbpWxyHTEbzMk/stream/audio.html?ID=63ab22f6725928067e8546d8f4119e87dcbd51f2)
